### Validate PraxisLabObservation — HbA1c quantitativ (LOINC + LDT, interpretation H)
# @name validate-lab-obs-hba1c
# Expected: OperationOutcome with "all ok" (no errors)
# Covers: dual coding LOINC+LDT, valueQuantity, referenceRange low/high UCUM, interpretation H, specimen reference
POST http://localhost:8080/fhir/Observation/$validate?profile=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/StructureDefinition/praxis-lab-observation
Authorization: Basic basic:secret
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Observation",
  "meta": {
    "profile": ["https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/StructureDefinition/praxis-lab-observation"]
  },
  "status": "final",
  "category": [
    {
      "coding": [
        {
          "system": "http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/observation-category",
          "code": "laboratory"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "code": {
    "coding": [
      {
        "system": "http://loinc.org",
        "code": "4548-4",
        "display": "Hemoglobin A1c/Hemoglobin.total in Blood"
      },
      {
        "system": "https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/NamingSystem/ldt-testkennungen",
        "code": "03034000",
        "display": "HbA1c"
      }
    ]
  },
  "subject": { "reference": "Patient/example-patient" },
  "effectiveDateTime": "2026-04-05T08:30:00+02:00",
  "valueQuantity": {
    "value": 6.1,
    "unit": "%",
    "system": "http://unitsofmeasure.org",
    "code": "%"
  },
  "interpretation": [
    {
      "coding": [
        {
          "system": "http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ObservationInterpretation",
          "code": "H",
          "display": "High"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "referenceRange": [
    {
      "low": {
        "value": 4.0,
        "unit": "%",
        "system": "http://unitsofmeasure.org",
        "code": "%"
      },
      "high": {
        "value": 6.0,
        "unit": "%",
        "system": "http://unitsofmeasure.org",
        "code": "%"
      }
    }
  ],
  "specimen": { "reference": "Specimen/example-specimen-blut-edta" }
}

?? status == 200


### Validate PraxisLabObservation — Leukozyten Urin qualitativ (LOINC + LDT, valueString, interpretation N)
